Unit TestingThe package artemis-junit provides tools to facilitate how to run Artemis resources inside Junit Tests.These are provided as junit rules and can make it easier to embed Messaging functionality on your tests.ExampleImport this on your pom.xml
  org.apache.activemq
  artemis-junit

  1.5.0
  test

Declare a rule on your JUnit Testimport org.apache.activemq.artemis.junit.EmbeddedJMSResource;
import org.junit.Rule;
import org.junit.Test;

public class MyTest {

   @Rule
   public EmbeddedJMSResource resource = new EmbeddedJMSResource();

   @Test
   public void myTest() {

   }
}
